{"tid":2179390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街 啱啱發現控制到個夢","createTime":"2020-08-29T05:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T14:06:56.000Z","uid":185842,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5f244364559889a8c9cc30f82b4f78b5d54eb8","tid":2179390,"uid":185842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母，啱啱係個夢知道控制到，準備爽下嘅時候，老豆打嚟嘈醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0d5293c72cb3541a13c20817c1d5b06970d41f","tid":2179390,"uid":148315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"之前有一排瞓覺前專登訓練自己發清醒夢<br />\n控制夢嘅機會真係多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢排懶咗直接瞓就冇咗呢個能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d0b9dd94567d46215e3f47e0292bdd5f18a7f0","tid":2179390,"uid":185842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec0d5293c72cb3541a13c20817c1d5b06970d41f","tid":2179390,"uid":148315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"之前有一排瞓覺前專登訓練自己發清醒夢<br />\n控制夢嘅機會真係多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj